    "Academic research on digital misinformation on social media has just lately started, despite the significant efforts of huge tech corporations (Pérez Dasilva et al. 2021).",
    "In this section, we examine the literature on the creation and dissemination of online text, particularly fake news on social media networks.",
    "Relevant state of the art is presented in the following, where main findings are also highlighted for each reviewed contribution.",
    "The study in Ahmed (2021) provides insights into the unintentional sharing of deep fakes and emphasizes the importance of political interest, a major driver of political involvement and a factor that is positively correlated with deep fake sharing.",
